name: John IZZI v. Ben WEISS et al.

parties: John IZZI v. Ben WEISS et al.

opinions.text:
ORDER
The defendants’ brief having been filed, plaintiff’s motion to dismiss this appeal for lack of prosecution is denied.

attorneys: Louis J. Vallone, John J. Vallone, Jr., Providence, for plaintiff.
Friedman & Kessler, Harold I. Kessler, Providence, for defendants.

Friedman & Kessler, Harold I. Kessler, Providence, for defendants.
